   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE visibility_level = 0

   UNION ALL

   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE visibility_level = 1
      AND 1785 IS NOT NULL

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1785
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 2

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
LEFT JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1785 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 3
      AND (gu.id IS NOT NULL OR FALSE)

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = 1785 AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.visibility_level = 4
 )
) ORDER BY name ASC
